<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 21 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at the
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1764.84 Tuesday, up 0.36 points
from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,039,594 shares changed hands in 832 deals, and the
turnover was 3.4 billion rials (about 1.1 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
In the trading, shares of 28 companies mades gains, and those
of 21 others declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
