<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, September 21 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 690.45 points Tuesday, up 0.60 percent from Monday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
A daily bulletin of the bourse said 64,746 shares changed hands
in 8,989 deals, and the turnover was 1,189,839 dinars (1.08
million U.S. dollars). 
</P>
