<HEADLINE> Chirac Expresses Condolences Over Victims of </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, September 21 (Xinhua) -- French President Jacques Chirac
has expressed his deep condolences over thousands of people who
died in a strong earthquake which struck Chinese Taiwan early
Tuesday morning.
</P>
