Congolese crisis.
</P>
<P>
"We met San Egidio Community's delegation and we discussed
their proposal to be the facilitator in the future national debate
suggested in the Lusaka peace accord," Moise Nyarugabo, the
Vice-President of the main Congolese rebel movement, the Congolese
Rally for Democracy (RCD) told Rwanda News Agency RNA on Tuesday.
</P>
