and that no final response by the RCD was given to Don Matteo
Zuppi who was leading the delegation.
</P>
<P>
San Egidio Community achieved its fame in negotiating the end
to the war in Mozambique between ruling Frelimo and rebel Renamo
parties.
</P>
<P>
"We are discussing the opportunity offered to us by San Egidio
Community. We will give our response to their initiative in the
coming days," Nyarugabo told RNA.
</P>
<P>
Political analysts said that the RCD will reject the mediation
of San Egidio Community for it is seen as close to President
fighting to President Laurent Desire Kabila.
</P>
<P>
"The choice of a mediator is an affair of Congolese. None can
impose us any person we have not agreed upon," Nyarugabo
highlighted.
</P>
<P>
He said that the Organization of African Unity (OAU) could play
a greater role in bringing together all parties to the Congolese
crisis so that they can discuss and convene on a mediator.
</P>
<P>
''Its (OAU) role would be to coordinate and harmonize different
 proposals regarding the mediator, the venue, and the
participants," Nyarugabo told RNA. 
