<HEADLINE> Pakistan Govt Says Enjoying Good Ties With Army </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, September 22 (Xinhua) -- The Pakistani government
Wednesday said it enjoys complete harmony with the country's
powerful armed forces.
</P>
<P>
"There is complete harmony and cooperation between all the
sections of the government of Pakistan including all of its
civilian and non-civilian components," Pakistani Information
Minister Mushahid Hussain told newsmen after a cabinet meeting
chaired by Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif.
</P>
<P>
