<HEADLINE> Xinhua Photo List for September 22 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 22 (Xinhua) -- Following is a list of photos
released by Xinhua today:
</P>
<P>
1. Chinese President Jiang Zemin and Premier Zhu Rongji talk at
the 4th Plenary Session of the 15th Central Committee of the
Communist Party of China (CPC) held in Beijing September 19-22.
2. Picture shows the conference hall where the 4th Plenary Session
of the 15th Central Committee of the Communist Party of China (CPC)
was held in Beijing September 19-22.
3. Hu Jintao, a member of the Standing Committee of the Political
Bureau of the 15th Central Committee of the Communist Party of
China (CPC) and State vice-President, has been appointed vice-
Chairman of the Central Military Commission (CMC) at the 4th
Plenary Session of the 15th CPC Central Committee held in Beijing
from September 19-22.
4. Soldiers stationed in Shanghai stand in a circle with a large
moon cake in the middle as they celebrate the upcoming Mid-autumn
Festival Shanghai, September 22. The moon cake, 1.06 meters thick
and 3.67 meters in diameter, weighs 5474 kilograms. The
traditional moon festival will fall on September 24.
5. Two visitors look at a picture of Deng Xiaoping as they tour
the grand picture exhibition presenting the achievement of China
in the past 50 years, Nanjing, capital of Jiangsu Province,
September 22.
6. The Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference(CPPCC)
celebrates its 50th founding anniversary in Beijing, September 22.
7. Chinese President Jiang Zemin meets with James Carlisle,
governor-general of Antigua and Barbuda in Beijing September 22.
8. Chinese President Jiang Zemin delivers a speech at the
celebration for the 50th anniversary of the founding of the
Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC) held in
Beijing, September 22.
9. Chinese Vice-Premier Li Lanqing meets with Lee Kuan Yew, Senior
Minister of Prime Minister's Office, also former Prime Minister of
Singapore, in Beijing, September 22.
10. A staff member with Guizhou Museum sorts out dinosaur fossil
recently found in Chengguan township, Pingba county of Guizhou
province, September 22. 
</P>
