Jenny Shipley has shown her sympathy to the earthquake-hit people
in Taiwan.
</P>
<P>
In a statement issued here on Wednesday by the Prime Minister's
Office, Mrs. Shipley said the thoughts of New Zealanders are with
the people in Taiwan as they come to terms with the impact of
Tuesday's destructive earthquake.
</P>
