<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, September 21 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Foreign
Minister Tang Jiaxuan on Tuesday met his counterparts from the
United Arab Emirates, Saudi Arabia, Kuwait, Oman, Bahrain, Qatar,
the members of the cooperation Council for the Arab State of the
Gulf(GCC).
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, Tang Jiaxuan said China was willing to
further develop friendly relations with these countries and GCC at
the basis of mutual respect and equality.
</P>
<P>
